{"level":"N3","levelName":"N3","levelNameCn":"中级","emoji":"🌳","quizzes":[{"id":"n3-q-001","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"grammar","question":"「日本語は勉強すればするほど面白くなる」是什么意思？","emoji":"📝","options":[{"id":"a","text":"日语越学越有趣","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"日语学了也没意思","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"日语不学也有趣","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"日语学一次就够了","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「～ば～ほど」表示「越～越～」。所以是「越学越有趣」。","sourceRef":"n3-g-001"},{"id":"n3-q-002","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"vocabulary","question":"「経験」的读音是？","emoji":"🔊","options":[{"id":"a","text":"けいけん","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"けいかん","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"きょうけん","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"けけん","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「経験」读作「けいけん」。注意长音。","sourceRef":"n3-v-002"}]}
